source.name: Maryland Total New Parcels For Residential Development: 2006- 2009
source.description:
Maryland Total New Parcels for Residential Development from 2006 to 2009 based on MDProperty View 2009 Edition and Priority Funding Areas (PFA) Boundaries as of May 2011.
Priority Funding Areas are existing communities and places where local governments want State investment to support future growth.
